qas.question: What is the largest library in the United States?
What is the second largest library in the US?
What is the name of the library system in Queens?
What is Brooklyn's public library system called?
Along with Staten Island and the Bronx, what borough is served by the New York Public Library?

context: <a0_0>The New York Public Library<a0_0/>, which has the largest collection of any public library system in the United States, serves <a4_0>Manhattan<a4_0/>, the Bronx, and Staten Island. Queens is served by the <a1_0><a2_0>Queens Borough Public Library<a2_0/><a1_0/>, the nation's second largest public library system, while the <a3_0>Brooklyn Public Library<a3_0/> serves Brooklyn.
